				<div id="about">
					<h2>About the Sports Day</h2>
					<p>Set up by Maria Langslow in 2015, the Didsbury Big Sports Day is an annual summer event at Didsbury Park, all in the name of the eating disorder charity b-eat. The event was a huge success this year, raising more than &pound;200.</p>
					<p>Sports that were on display included British Military Fitness, Zumba, Fencing and American Football. All these sports are returning, with more sports lined up to give you a taste of what's out there in 2016.</p>
					<p>There's also drinks available, as well as the return of the hugely popular bake sale.</p>
				</div>
